        "data": "<p>Published: December 16, 2019</p>\n<p>We would like to inform you that the Liferay Commerce documentation has been updated and is now available on a new site:<span> </span><span><a href=\"https://discover.liferay.com/e2t/c/*W3T8XKT8WznNlW38QJkF6FSwz20/*W5t2H7v71sMPsVJpPFK57Czyd0/5/f18dQhb0SfHB8YXNlsW43dbxH7PKkCqW56NNCW2z9bNSW2KBfjg6mdtshW2_YYBC8YjSpXW30THSS8-y10rW8_dDry4bH_qwW2N33B53_t0gLW32Gf2Q4dy5FSW1kXfyt1SdKWJW1m2pz42VvJdhW2JDgVL1ZcjVfW1txG9N6GsfdKW8XNh8_7J_KVBW586mYC2JXNJpN7k1Y8dsfSyHW1vPdkl7qZD8RW1X8K5v214hLPW1BqBGT46SRxBW7lJz5_1K3nFKW7B1tSC1xfjdhW7s5BSr1Wvhx_W1xZ72w7kwZdDW8X0Twg20pBhcW1Gb5fs7vW9PTVyFcyQ5HFzhYW7dr9qW72YqDyW8pk4Kv5L1qjnW3vGR5s6R0xBVW1m13Gx49FShzW1V5SWx9lrSMqW5F1q8D4dxJp_W9dq3vK5N89PwW2Dw8PP7D39z0W3wPByY3wqspBf832Fcs11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://discover.liferay.com/e2t/c/*W3T8XKT8WznNlW38QJkF6FSwz20/*W5t2H7v71sMPsVJpPFK57Czyd0/5/f18dQhb0SfHB8YXNlsW43dbxH7PKkCqW56NNCW2z9bNSW2KBfjg6mdtshW2_YYBC8YjSpXW30THSS8-y10rW8_dDry4bH_qwW2N33B53_t0gLW32Gf2Q4dy5FSW1kXfyt1SdKWJW1m2pz42VvJdhW2JDgVL1ZcjVfW1txG9N6GsfdKW8XNh8_7J_KVBW586mYC2JXNJpN7k1Y8dsfSyHW1vPdkl7qZD8RW1X8K5v214hLPW1BqBGT46SRxBW7lJz5_1K3nFKW7B1tSC1xfjdhW7s5BSr1Wvhx_W1xZ72w7kwZdDW8X0Twg20pBhcW1Gb5fs7vW9PTVyFcyQ5HFzhYW7dr9qW72YqDyW8pk4Kv5L1qjnW3vGR5s6R0xBVW1m13Gx49FShzW1V5SWx9lrSMqW5F1q8D4dxJp_W9dq3vK5N89PwW2Dw8PP7D39z0W3wPByY3wqspBf832Fcs11&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1576594659894000&amp;usg=AFQjCNH9Z42XeYcGUQtdDBoZNmv-QLACEg\">learn.liferay.com</a></span>.</p>\n<p>The new documentation includes a full revamp of the structure and content along with more intuitive categorizations for articles, new development tutorials, and expanded walkthroughs of Liferay Commerce features.</p>\n<p>Please let us know what you think, and we hope that these updates will enhance your experience of learning and using Liferay Commerce.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/commerce/2.x/en/index.html\" target=\"_self\">Learn More</a></p>"
